  rdfs:comment           "Microvessel densities\nwere significantly reduced in Gabrb3ECKO cortex in comparison\nwith Gabrb3fl/fl cortex. Additionally,\nvessel diameters were markedly increased in Gabrb3ECKO\ncortex indicative of morphological alterations when compared\nto controls" ;
